snippet.textDisplay: This is indeed the most powerful song/kalaam  of CS History. No one can sing  more better than Madam Abida Parveen. words are less for her praise. Excellent energetic fit music by Shani Arshad. I thought it was some poet's kalaam but this was written on the spot. Mannu, the ever green soul of CS, brilliant. Overall everything is so much brilliant that there is no word in dictionary to describe how beautiful this song/kalaam is. ❤❤❤
